the wild monkey from the woods.

141
00:15:06,805 --> 00:15:09,689
And her husband-to-be, huh?

142
00:15:11,811 --> 00:15:13,556
Still got that foul mouth, huh?

143
00:15:15,108 --> 00:15:18,245
Don’t make me shut that mouth with your own blood.

144
00:15:18,564 --> 00:15:21,489
Ignore him, Loy. He's just barking.

145
00:15:22,228 --> 00:15:26,056
If we fight him,
his blood will just get on our feet.

146
00:15:29,310 --> 00:15:30,930
Someone's feisty today.

147
00:15:34,040 --> 00:15:35,582
What do you want?

148
00:15:36,452 --> 00:15:39,134
We were just walking past,
minding our business...

149
00:15:39,672 --> 00:15:42,475
And we heard a loud commotion.

150
00:15:43,576 --> 00:15:44,927
So we came to check it out.

151
00:15:46,980 --> 00:15:49,667
- That's how we found out.
- Know what?

152
00:15:50,693 --> 00:15:56,555
That's how we know that this year's
Wai Kru ceremony at Master Jom's place...

153
00:15:57,957 --> 00:16:02,286
The dancers skipped out to get drunk.

154
00:16:03,725 --> 00:16:05,990
And it's gonna ruin the Wai Kru thing.

155
00:16:09,794 --> 00:16:11,733
I think, this year...

156
00:16:12,247 --> 00:16:17,092
Master Jom and his crew are gonna be
so embarrassed 'cause of these drunk students.

157
00:16:17,631 --> 00:16:18,982
Drunks.

158
00:16:18,995 --> 00:16:21,556
Well, looks like you're right this time, Lert.

159
00:16:22,664 --> 00:16:24,766
- Oh, hey Mae Bua, where the hell have you been?
-  Butt out!

160
00:16:26,906 --> 00:16:29,649
Honestly, I wasn't planning
on agreeing with you guys.

161
00:16:30,363 --> 00:16:32,477
But I gotta admit, what you said’s true.

162
00:16:33,891 --> 00:16:37,588
If anyone's at fault, it's me.

163
00:16:40,479 --> 00:16:42,006
Because I'm poor.

164
00:16:46,079 --> 00:16:50,220
That's how poor people are.

165
00:17:01,062 --> 00:17:04,168
Do I look dead, Wan?
It's just a little cut on my head.

166
00:17:04,394 --> 00:17:06,902
-  Let me have a look.
-  Ouch, that really hurts.

167
00:17:23,542 --> 00:17:28,165
Loy, this is my fault. I'm sorry.
